CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 1, 1947, pg. 18, reads: "Hill City Scouts - A group of Girl Scouts, active at Hill City Municipality, were photographed at a meeting last week. Included in the picture are: Lillian Morris, president; Gladys Moore, Catherine Smith, Sarah Anderson, Ernestine Payne, LuVerne and Gloria Bucy, Beverly Lewis, Arlene Gurham, Delores Jones, Dolores Hunter and Mildred Payne. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Hill City Girl Scouts, including president Lillian Morris, Gladys Moore, Catherine Smith, Sarah Anderson, Ernestine Payne, LuVerne Bucy, Gloria Bucy, Beverly Lewis, Arlene Gurham, Delores Jones, Dolores Hunter, and Mildred Payne seated in circle for meeting
